title: Want To Buy:  Mosin Nagant Expert with Proven Experience in Mounting Scopes, etc
postcontent:
I'm looking for a local expert in Louisville who knows how to mill/drill/tap an ATI scope mount for a mosin nagant, can install steel scope rings, install a scope, and site in a scope.  I also need a new stock placed on the gun and a new trigger pull installed.  I'm basically asking for a new gun with all of the parts that I supply. 

I'm not looking for someone who thinks they can do it.  I know how to do it myself but I'm looking for someone who has experience and KNOWS they can do it because they've done it before.  This is going to be my primary deer rifle and I want something that is 100% top of the line.  I want your experience and your know-how.  If you've only done this one or twice then this is NOT FOR YOU.  If you know what you're doing then I want to hear from you.

Your job:

Replace stock with ATI stock (some sanding may be needed)
Install ATI scope mount (you will need drill press - but you already know this if you've done this before)
Install steel scope rings 
Install scope
Site in scope (will provide you ammo)
Install new trigger pull 
Grind off and re-blue the front site (and area) since it's no longer needed
Install new bolt handle from provided kit (will need machined)
Clean and lube gun from top to bottom
Check AND verify headspace - this is a must
Provide me with leftover parts unless you want to discount your service in exchange for these leftovers

My job:
Provide you with standard gun
Provide you with all of the above parts needed
Provide you with ammo to site gun
Pay you for your experience and time.  Will be willing to trade for mags, ammo, or best of all -- CASH.

If you can perform this, please contact me so we can speak.  I'm looking to make this my primary rifle and this is important to me.  We can trade/wheel N deal/ or I can just flat out pay.  

Looking forward to hearing from you.
